'''埃米·维维安·科尼·巴雷特'''（{{lang-en|Amy Vivian Coney Barrett}}， {{bd|1972年|1月28日|||catIdx=B}}）<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/politics/2020/9/25/21454492/who-is-amy-coney-barrett-meet-trumps-leading-supreme-court-pick |script-title=en:Who is Amy Coney Barrett? Meet Trump’s Supreme Court pick |quote=Name: Amy Coney Barrett；Age: 48, Born Jan. 28, 1972 |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927074141/https://chicago.suntimes.com/politics/2020/9/25/21454492/who-is-amy-coney-barrett-meet-trumps-leading-supreme-court-pick |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="National Catholic Register (2017)">{{cite news |author = Editors |title = JFK, Amy Coney Barrett and Anti-Catholicism |date = 2017-09-22 |newspaper = National Catholic Register |url = http://www.ncregister.com/daily-news/jfk-amy-coney-barrett-and-anti-catholicism |access-date = 2017-10-07 |archive-url = https://archive.today/20171007150736/http://www.ncregister.com/daily-news/jfk-amy-coney-barrett-and-anti-catholicism |archive-date = 2017-10-07 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="FJC Bio">{{Cite web|url=https://www.fjc.gov/history/judges/barrett-amy-coney|title=Barrett, Amy Coney {{!}} Federal Judicial Center|website=www.fjc.gov|language=en|access-date=2018-07-07|archive-date=2018-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180707230535/https://www.fjc.gov/history/judges/barrett-amy-coney|dead-url=no}}</ref>是[[美國聯邦第七巡迴上訴法院|美國聯邦第七巡迴上訴法院]]法官，2017年獲美國總統[[唐納·川普|特朗普]]提名出任此職。曾擔任[[安東寧·斯卡利亞|安東寧·斯卡利亞]]的法官助理。2020年9月26日，总统特朗普提名巴雷特为[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]大法官<ref name="official SCOTUS">{{cite web |author1=Steve Holland |author2=Lawrence Hurley |author3=Andrew Chung |title=Trump announces 'brilliant' conservative judge Barrett as Supreme Court pick |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-court-trump/trump-announces-brilliant-conservative-judge-barrett-as-supreme-court-pick-idUSKBN26H0GI |website=reuters.com |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926214309/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-court-trump/trump-announces-brilliant-conservative-judge-barrett-as-supreme-court-pick-idUSKBN26H0GI |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Trump picks conservative Amy Coney Barrett for Supreme Court|url=https://apnews.com/article/us-supreme-court-michael-pence-archive-courts-donald-trump-e2678a13cf3d2383300db6f1416664d6|accessdate=2020-09-26|date=2020-09-26|author1=Zeke Miller|author2=Lisa Mascaro|author3=Mary Clare Jalonick|authorlink1=Zeke Miller|website=apnews.com|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926080704/https://apnews.com/article/us-supreme-court-michael-pence-archive-courts-donald-trump-e2678a13cf3d2383300db6f1416664d6|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 2020年10月26日，[[美国参议院|美国参议院]]通过巴雷特的提名後随即宣誓，48歲的巴雷特成为[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]第115任大法官<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Senate Confirms Amy Coney Barrett for Supreme Court|url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/articles/senate-confirms-amy-coney-barrett-supreme-court/|accessdate=2020-10-27|author=|date=2020-10-26|format=|publisher=whitehouse.gov|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027065321/https://www.whitehouse.gov/articles/senate-confirms-amy-coney-barrett-supreme-court/|archivedate=2020-10-27}}</ref>。

== 介绍 ==
埃米·维维安·科尼·巴雷特生于1972年1月28日，出生地为[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]。<ref name="FJC Bio"/>她是父母七名子女中的长女，有五个妹妹和一个弟弟。其父迈克尔·康尼曾是[[荷兰皇家壳牌|壳牌]]石油公司的律师，母亲是一位家庭主妇。艾米在新奥尔良城郊的梅泰里地区长大，1990年毕业于圣玛利多明我高中。<ref>{{cite web|title=Amy Coney Barrett: Mother of 7, Metairie native, solid conservative ... next Supreme Court justice?|url=https://www.nola.com/article_d71cb604-ae33-5892-8848-04d2113bd7a6.html|accessdate=|author=|date=2018-07-06|format=|work=The Times-Picayune/The New Orleans Advocate|publisher=|language=en|last1=Stole|first1=Bryn|access-date=2020-09-22|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926001500/https://www.nola.com/article_d71cb604-ae33-5892-8848-04d2113bd7a6.html}}</ref>

艾米随后在田纳西州[[孟菲斯|孟菲斯]]的罗德学院学习英语文学。1994年以优异成绩获得文学学士学位，加入美国大学优等生荣誉学会。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.scotusblog.com/2018/07/potential-nominee-profile-amy-coney-barrett/|title=Potential nominee profile: Amy Coney Barrett|date=2018-07-04|work=SCOTUSblog|access-date=2018-07-07|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706122744/http://www.scotusblog.com/2018/07/potential-nominee-profile-amy-coney-barrett/|author=|publisher=|accessdate=|format=}}</ref>之后，艾米在[[圣母大学法学院|圣母大学法学院]]就读，获得了全额奖学金。曾担任刊物《圣母大学法学评论》的执行编辑。<ref name=Howe>Amy Howe, [https://www.scotusblog.com/2020/09/profile-of-a-potential-nominee-amy-coney-barrett/ Profile of a potential nominee: Amy Coney Barrett] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923064836/https://www.scotusblog.com/2020/09/profile-of-a-potential-nominee-amy-coney-barrett/ |date=2020-09-23 }}, ''SCOTUSblog'' (September 21, 2020).</ref>1997年以全班第一名的最优异成绩毕业并获得法律博士学位。<ref name=":3">{{cite web|title=Hon. Amy Coney Barrett, Professor of Law|url=https://law.nd.edu/directory/amy-barrett/|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=University of Notre Dame School of Law|language=|access-date=2019-03-14|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402042112/https://law.nd.edu/directory/amy-barrett/}}</ref>

2020年10月26日，[[美國參議院|美國參議院]]以52票对48票批准巴雷特出任美国最高法院大法官，亦是150年来首位沒有獲得參議院少数党議員支持的大法官。當晚，巴雷特在[[白宮|白宮]]宣誓就職，成為川普任內第三位就職的大法官。<ref>{{cite news |title=获参议院批准后 巴雷特宣誓就任美国最高法院大法官 |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/barret-supreme-court-senate-confirmation-20201026/5637019.html |accessdate=2020-10-27 |archive-date=2020-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118093746/https://www.voachinese.com/a/barret-supreme-court-senate-confirmation-20201026/5637019.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":1" />

== 立场 ==
巴雷特信奉美国[[宪法原典主义|宪法原典主义]]，在2019年一场于[[凯斯西储大学|凯斯西储大学]]宣讲的课程中，她说道：“法官必须遵循宪法典章的原初公共意涵。”该流派信奉已故大法官[[安東寧·斯卡利亞|斯卡利亚]]的见解“法律治国，而非立法者治国”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Amy Coney Barrett and the Scalia Standard|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/amy-coney-barrett-and-the-scalia-standard-11601315588|accessdate=2020-09-30|author=James Freeman|date=2020-09-28|format=|publisher=WSJ|language=英语|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111012337/https://www.wsj.com/articles/amy-coney-barrett-and-the-scalia-standard-11601315588|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同时，巴雷特是一名反对[[LGBTQ|LGBTQ]]權利、反[[同婚|同婚]]以及[[堕胎|堕胎]]的[[保守派|保守派]]，深受保守派的青睐，與前任大法官[[露絲·貝德·金斯堡|-{zh-cn:露丝·贝德尔·金斯伯格;zh-tw:露絲·貝德·金斯伯格;zh-hk:露芙·巴達·堅士堡;}-]]的風格及立場十分不同<ref>{{Cite web|title=快讯！美参议院投票通过巴雷特的大法官提名|url=https://m.haiwainet.cn/ttc/3541093/2020/1027/content_31902843_1.html?tt_group_id=6888084693493907981|accessdate=2020-10-27|author=|date=2020-10-27|format=|publisher=海外网|language=zh|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027070901/https://m.haiwainet.cn/ttc/3541093/2020/1027/content_31902843_1.html?tt_group_id=6888084693493907981|archivedate=2020-10-27}}</ref>。[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]的一篇评论指出，美国保守人士将巴雷特视为斯卡利亚在最高法院的继承者<ref>{{Cite web|title=For Conservative Christian Women, Amy Coney Barrett’s Success Is Personal|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/28/us/amy-coney-barrett-christian-women.html|accessdate=2020-09-30|author=Ruth Graham|date=2020-09-28|format=|publisher=New York Times|language=英语|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223023010/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/28/us/amy-coney-barrett-christian-women.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

